        </blockquote>
        <blockquote>
<a href="http://www.disp.uniroma2.it/users/italiano/ads13/">ADS 2013: 6th Bertinoro Workshop on Algorithms and Data Structures</a> (2-7 June 2013)
        </blockquote>

